{"tid":720971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔雙重標準嘅極致","createTime":"2018-06-28T10:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T06:25:45.000Z","uid":35870,"like":32,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0e5b1f16655f2cdbe0f7f43150e1e16956138d9","tid":720971,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 連登仔<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前，當公民黨提出要立空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 政府邊會立？政府邊會想樓價跌？個個高官拎住幾廿層樓既得利益者，有用嘅野政府邊會做？<br />\n<br />\n近一兩個月，當有報紙吹風話政府研究緊空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 研究到2046 d官放晒都未落實到啦！政府邊會想樓價跌？<br />\n<br />\n再近一兩個星期，空置稅好似真係會落實<br />\n連登仔: 有撚用咩一手空置稅，係就搞埋二手空置稅啦！唉，不過政府個個幾廿層樓，邊想樓價跌？<br />\n<br />\n今日，好似話林鄭準備開行會出招整個一手空置稅<br />\n連登仔: 出埋d廢招，樓價繼續升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟係連登仔心目中，空置稅有無用架呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊陣時高登就係畀唔到呢d樂趣人，望到連登仔任擺龍門，真係打從心底入面笑出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba1e4392d72a6f601801523b2473081ce987c01","tid":720971,"uid":21423,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:52:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9805343e8342643c5c511a5180ed75c9cc49af4c","tid":720971,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"梁振英年代出辣招前:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 政府任人炒樓炒到貴晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出辣招後:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 政府出招托市<img src=\"/assets/faces/n